Score computation defines PRISM properties to check against the formal models of pathways. These properties are sought to find the possibility that the final effector genes (final genes that trigger cell responses) are differentially activated; that is, they are in state 4. This property is defined in PRISM language as:10\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
