				\begin{document}$$ P=?\left[F\ \left(g=4\right)\right] $$\end{document}P=?Fg=4where F is a temporal operator means eventually in the future, and g is a final effector gene. These probabilities are computed for every final effector genes of the pathway path, and their sum is used to assign a score to each pathway as follows:11\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
